# Default-deny: ignore everything, then allow-list what belongs in the repo.
*
!*/
!.gitignore
# source of truth + tooling
!*.py
!Makefile
!install.sh
!*.md
# generated man pages (committed so `git clone && ./install.sh` needs no build)
!man7/*.7
# bundled KEV snapshot (refreshed by `make regen`)
!data/known_exploited_vulnerabilities.csv
